Invocation Name: wednesday coin
des: Welcome to WednesdayCoin, a skill that helps you learn about WednesdayCoin and Wednesdays! WednesdayCoin is an ERC20 token that can only be sent on Wednesdays. This helper skill will let you know when it is Wednesday UTC, and teach you more about Wednesdays.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
